metadata.name: Flying To The Moon
metadata.description:
“Flying To The Moon”  
by Matthias Doppler  
 Digital painting 
Resolution: 6100px x 6100px  
 Format: PNG

The first person to obtain this work will receive a signed 1/1 print of the artwork which will not be sold anywhere else.

I will attach a certificate of authenticity that links the physical work with the NFT on the blockchain.

Artwork will be printed on high quality textured Hahnemühle German etching paper with a weight of 310gsm.

The winning bidder must be able to contact me after winning the auction so I know where to send the print (verify twitter to avoid confusion).

Please tell me what size you would like the print (max. 28" x 28" / 711mm x 711mm to insure the highest possible quality).
